<CATEGORY> sports </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Rain Postpones NHRA Session </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BRISTOL, Tenn. (AP) -- Rain forced postponement Saturday of the  
NHRA's Winston Showdown at Bristol Dragway. 
</P>
<P>
	The all-star race between dragsters and funny cars was set back  
to Sunday. 
  	   	
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
