<HEADLINE> Cowboys QB Aikman Gets Engaged </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	DALLAS (AP) -- Dallas Cowboys quarterback Troy Aikman has become  
engaged to a former employee of the team's public relations 
department, according to The Dallas Morning News. 
</P>
<P>
	The newspaper reported in its Saturday editions that Aikman and  
Rhonda Worthey had been dating for nearly a year. 
</P>
<P>
	Worthey was wearing a large diamond ring when the couple  
returned from a California vacation. 
</P>
<P>
	No wedding date has been set, but it will be after the NFL  
season ends in January, the News reported. 
</P>
<P>
