Steinberg and Aikman Enterprises were not returned to The 
Associated Press on Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
	The couple met at Valley Ranch, where Worthey worked until she  
resigned several months ago to devote fulltime to her 9-year-old 
daughter, the newspaper reported. 
</P>
<P>
	Aikman, 32, has never been married. Worthey is 30.  
  	   	
