<HEADLINE>  Rapids 2, United 1 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- Jorge Dely Valdes' goal broke a tie in the  
74th minute as the Colorado Rapids beat D.C. United 2-1 Saturday 
night in a match between MLS conference leaders. 
</P>
