man they arrested and allegedly took in handcuffs to a remote 
parking lot. The patrolmen, Daniel Bolanos and Rolando Bolanos Jr., 
surrendered yesterday. They are accused of beating Yoel Pacheco in 
November after taking him to the lot near the Hialeah Park 
racetrack, and then trying to cover it up with false police 
reports. 

